Subject: Re: [VB] Middle seat fit


> The question has come up as to whether a full length middle seat from a '70s
> Bay window will fit into a '67 split.  Anyone know for sure?

Yes it will bolt right in. BTDT

That is, if you have the keyholes at the edge by the cargo doors. A walk-thru is
set up for a 3/4 seat. A non-walk-thru is set up for a full seat.

